{"tid":58509,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾鈺成：來自北京的七言詩估特首選情","createTime":"2016-12-29T01:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T06:20:02.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4c3cc8e4eb33a307082bca6d9ead1d6eb40b991","tid":58509,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T01:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/29/091816_a1fabd0b28ad7f7de90006a634e6aa4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F29%2F091816_a1fabd0b28ad7f7de90006a634e6aa4f.jpg&h=a9e7c9b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首選舉動向備受全城關注，作為熱門潛在人選之一的立法會前主席曾鈺成引述一首據稱來自京城消息人士而謎底同選情有關的七言絕詩，一向愛玩文字遊戲的曾鈺成仲逐句拆解，從字裏行間猜度有機會勝出的人選，但曾鈺成亦強調這只是講求娛樂性、不講真實性的穿鑿附會。<br />\n<br />\n曾鈺成今日在《am730》專欄的文章取題為《不用當真》，刊出由友人轉告的這首來自北京的蘇東坡七言絕句：<br />\n<br />\n黑雲翻墨未遮山，白雨跳珠亂入船。<br />\n<br />\n捲地風來忽吹散，望湖樓下水如天。<br />\n<br />\n曾鈺成先解釋詩的內容，開始是描寫烏雲蔽日，但並未遮蓋眼前山巒；接着是驟雨來到，雨點打在詩人的船上；忽然颳起一陣風，吹散雲和雨，雨過天青，望湖樓下水平如鏡。<br />\n<br />\n他之後從一個「較為有趣」的角度解讀詩的內容：首句「黑雲翻墨」，可否解作對某人抹黑，或者指某人「當黑」，遇到很大的困難？而「未遮山」則指抹黑並不成功，或者某人未有被困難所阻？<br />\n<br />\n第二句的「亂入船」，曾鈺成認為顯然是說有若干不應參選的人搶着參選，至於是誰，或者可以從「白雨跳珠」猜出端倪：那是白色的雨，不是黃色、藍色，也不是紅色。<br />\n<br />\n第三句最重要的是「忽」字，含有突如其來，令人意想不到的意思。「捲地風」倏忽間便驅散了黑雲，吹停了白雨；曾鈺成就問這風來自何處、為何有這麼大威力呢？<br />\n<br />\n曾鈺成為最後一句最有趣，指若解通這句，就應該知道誰是下任特首。「望湖樓下」，曾鈺成指現在已宣布參選的有胡國興、葉劉淑儀二人，「難道民『望』在『湖樓』(胡、劉)以『下』的，反而有機會勝出，『命水』如天？」<br />\n<br />\n曾鈺成雖然把全首詩拆解了，但他又明言這都是「穿鑿附會，為博讀者一哂，只求娛樂性，不講真實性」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161229/s00001/1482971954823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161229%2Fs00001%2F1482971954823&d=E3fy1ovkgYbkuPBlE3JVi4scwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=294c719c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161229%2Fs00001%2F1482971954823&h=b4090425\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161229/s00001/1482971954823</a>"},{"pid":"335ef19abd1eb3d7b67185fa2baa2f5e77536ffb","tid":58509,"uid":61075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T01:25:52.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"a3652780b6c94a177645d4497d416f10e1ea95cc","tid":58509,"uid":37384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T01:33:24.000Z","msg":"暗示品客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"12810a2baa29b6fcf59eff1d16c6035824b32f69","tid":58509,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T01:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee1fd9de92f9ad114c9cef43516bdeaa30310be","tid":58509,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:04:45.000Z","msg":"胡劉食得好應"},{"pid":"fdcbf8424dfddd8e4d57a474e99ffe2d93809e45","tid":58509,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:16:19.000Z","msg":"第一句係咪話要小心燒生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac8f3543293f91cb86c7cea32c68652ff944af4","tid":58509,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:27:35.000Z","msg":"唔小心跌左個1蚊:("},{"pid":"de1cba1adc20b42a2cd570e9b741cfb85b68d51d","tid":58509,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:34:30.000Z","msg":"照計就係林鄭"},{"pid":"22e2ee9049692dc43578dcbeee82da1b2b2d3740","tid":58509,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:35:42.000Z","msg":"第一句，意思係<br />\n還看燒生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0cb05c0317dbaf0867c68409eb5973b1f1abfb","tid":58509,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:44:40.000Z","msg":"党都知燒山威力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=